   The OIDs are being independently registered in the IANA registry "SMI
   Security for Cryptographic Algorithms" in [<a href=3D"https://www.rfc-ed=
itor.org/rfc/rfc8411" title=3D"&quot;IANA Registration for the Cryptographi=
